Recommends: avahi-daemon
Description: Linux CUPS driver for the Ricoh Aficio SP C240SF (DDST/GDI)
 Native C CUPS filter that converts CUPS raster input to the
 proprietary DDST stream understood by the Ricoh Aficio SP C240SF
 color laser MFP. Includes a PPD with the printer's paper sizes,
 trays, color modes, and duplex options.
 .
 The filter is multi-threaded: it encodes the four CMYK JBIG planes
 of each band in parallel, so a 600 dpi A4 colour page is converted
 in well under a second on a modern CPU.
 .
 A udev rule auto-registers the printer in CUPS when plugged in via
 USB, so most users won't need to run lpadmin manually.
